<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Compte en attente d'approbation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #D32F2F, #B71C1C);
            color: white;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .loader {
            border: 4px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-top: 4px solid #fff;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #B71C1C;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Compte en attente d'approbation ⏳</h1>
        <p>Votre compte est en attente de validation par un administrateur.</p>
        <p>Vous recevrez un e-mail dès que votre compte sera approuvé.</p>
        <div class="loader"></div>
        <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="button">Retour à la connexion</a>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Redirection automatique vers la connexion après 15 secondes
        setTimeout(() => {
            window.location.href = "{{ path('app_login') }}";
        }, 15000);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
